&lt;Guardian Trustco Inc>, earlierreporting a 198 pct increase in full year earnings per share,said the outlook for 1987 is more modest.    The company said it has started a number of long-termgrowth projects which have a payback period exceeding one year.Guardian Trustco did not give a specific earnings forecast.    The company earlier reported 1986 net profit rose to2,853,000 dlrs or 1.25 dlrs a share, from year-earlier1,579,000 dlrs or 42 cts a share. Reuter&#3;